	<h1 class="title">谁规定巧克力饮品不能给孩子带来“一天的美好开端”？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-30 19:02:53 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19968/medium/19968.jpg?1451462513" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="19968" data-title="《谁规定巧克力饮品不能给孩子带来“一天的美好开端”？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/19968/medium/19968.jpg?1451462513" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/19968.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
